# 7. Roadmap Success Definition

cmdOS success is not only measured by technology.

Success means:

Users can express goals naturally.

AI can understand intent.

Agents can execute tasks.

Developers can extend capabilities.

Businesses can operate with AI.

---

# Summary

The cmdOS Roadmap Overview defines the strategic journey from foundation to AI-native operating system.

The roadmap starts by building reliable infrastructure.

It expands through products and developer ecosystems.

It reaches the final vision:

A world where humans communicate intent and AI systems execute real-world tasks.

This is the path toward the AI Execution Operating System.
